<subSubSection pageId="40" pageNumber="41" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="40.[151,1436,1034,1205]" pageId="40" pageNumber="41">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,315,1070,1096]" pageId="40" pageNumber="41">Remarks.</emphasis>
The host plant is unknown. However, the host gall, 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Monzen" authorityYear="1929" baseAuthorityName="Ashmead" baseAuthorityYear="1904" box="[888,1131,1070,1096]" class="Insecta" family="Cynipidae" genus="Trichagalma" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="40" pageNumber="41" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="serratae">
<emphasis box="[888,1131,1070,1096]" italics="true" pageId="40" pageNumber="41">Trichagalma serratae</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, develops on 
<taxonomicName baseAuthorityName="Monzen" baseAuthorityYear="1937" box="[1283,1436,1071,1097]" class="Insecta" family="Cecidomyiidae" genus="Ametrodiplosis" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="40" pageNumber="41" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="acutissima">
<emphasis box="[1283,1436,1071,1097]" italics="true" pageId="40" pageNumber="41">Q. acutissima</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName box="[199,340,1106,1133]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Fagaceae" genus="Quercus" kingdom="Plantae" order="Fagales" pageId="40" pageNumber="41" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="variabilis">
<emphasis box="[199,340,1106,1133]" italics="true" pageId="40" pageNumber="41">Q. variabilis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(sect. 
<taxonomicName box="[414,486,1107,1133]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Fagaceae" genus="Cerris" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Plantae" order="Fagales" pageId="40" pageNumber="41" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[414,486,1107,1133]" italics="true" pageId="40" pageNumber="41">Cerris</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
) (
<bibRefCitation author="Penzes, Z. &amp; Tang, C. - T. &amp; Stone, G. N. &amp; Nicholls, J. A. &amp; Schweger, S. &amp; Bozso, M. &amp; Melika, G." box="[509,720,1106,1133]" pageId="40" pageNumber="41" pagination="245 - 289" refId="ref49925" refString="Penzes, Z., Tang, C. - T., Stone, G. N., Nicholls, J. A., Schweger, S., Bozso, M. &amp; Melika, G. (2018) Current status of the oak gallwasp (Hymenoptera: Cynipidae: Cynipini) fauna of the Eastern Palaearctic and Oriental Regions. Zootaxa, 4433 (2), 245 - 289. https: // doi. org / 10.11646 / zootaxa. 4433.2.2" type="journal article" year="2018">
Pénzes 
<emphasis box="[596,645,1106,1132]" italics="true" pageId="40" pageNumber="41">et al</emphasis>
. 2018
</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="40" pageNumber="41" type="biology_ecology">
<paragraph blockId="40.[151,1436,1034,1205]" pageId="40" pageNumber="41">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,295,1142,1168]" pageId="40" pageNumber="41">Biology.</emphasis>
Reared from galls of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Monzen" authorityYear="1929" baseAuthorityName="Ashmead" baseAuthorityYear="1904" box="[543,787,1142,1168]" class="Insecta" family="Cynipidae" genus="Trichagalma" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="40" pageNumber="41" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="serratae">
<emphasis box="[543,787,1142,1168]" italics="true" pageId="40" pageNumber="41">Trichagalma serratae</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(generation unknown) on an undetermined 
<emphasis box="[1283,1383,1143,1169]" italics="true" pageId="40" pageNumber="41">
<taxonomicName box="[1283,1380,1143,1169]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Fagaceae" genus="Quercus" kingdom="Plantae" order="Fagales" pageId="40" pageNumber="41" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">Quercus</taxonomicName>
,
</emphasis>
presumably in section 
<taxonomicName authority="(Lobato-Vila et al. 2021 a)" baseAuthorityName="Lobato-Vila" baseAuthorityYear="2021" box="[368,742,1178,1205]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Fagaceae" genus="Cerris" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Plantae" order="Fagales" pageId="40" pageNumber="41" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[368,440,1179,1205]" italics="true" pageId="40" pageNumber="41">Cerris</emphasis>
(
<bibRefCitation author="Lobato-Vila, I. &amp; Wang, Y. &amp; Melika, G. &amp; Guo, R. &amp; Xiaoxue, J. &amp; Pujade-Villar, J." box="[454,734,1178,1205]" pageId="40" pageNumber="41" pagination="341 - 362" refId="ref46693" refString="Lobato-Vila, I., Wang, Y., Melika, G., Guo, R., Xiaoxue, J. &amp; Pujade-Villar, J. (2021 a) A review of the species in the genus Synergus Hartig (Hymenoptera: Cynipidae: Synergini) from mainland China, with an updated key to Eastern Palaearctic and Oriental species. Journal of Asia-Pacific Entomology, 24 (1), 341 - 362. https: // doi. org / 10.1016 / j. aspen. 2020.11.014" type="journal article" year="2021">
Lobato-Vila 
<emphasis box="[598,647,1178,1204]" italics="true" pageId="40" pageNumber="41">et al</emphasis>
. 2021a
</bibRefCitation>
)
</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
